author_ssm: Jasmine Larkin, 2018. Contents list compiled by Mary Elizabeth Lennon
unittitle_ssm: Frank Hentschker Collection of Off and Off-Off Broadway Ephemera
abstract_ssm: Dr. Frank Hentschker is a faculty member in the Theatre program at The Graduate Center, City University of New York, and serves as the Executive Director and Director of Programs at the Martin E. Segal Theatre Center. The collection contains Off and Off-Off Broadway ephemera Hentschker collected, including fliers, invitations, and programs. Materials date from 2004 to 2009.
